n><span style="line-height: 18.3999996185303px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height: 18.3999996185303px;">as a&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height: 14.9499998092651px;">{!Job_placement__c.Role__c}</span><span style="line-height: 14.9499998092651px;"> with The Challenge on the NCS Programme. </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 11.5px;"><span style="line-height: 14.9499998092651px;"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 11.5px;"><span style="line-height: 18.3999996185303px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b>T</b></span><span style="line-height: 18.3999996185303px;">here are two payment periods for different sections of the programme. </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 11.5px;"><span style="line-height: 18.3999996185303px;"><br></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; white-space: pre-wrap;"><b style="line-height: 18.3999996185303px;">Payment Period 1:&nbsp;Pay date 13 March</b></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="line-height: 18.3999996185303px;">This takes into account any work completed between 14 February and 1 March.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="line-height: 18.3999996185303px;"><br></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; white-space: pre-wrap;"><b><span style="line-height: 18.3999996185303px;">Payment Period 2: Pay date </span><span style="line-height: 18.3999996185303px;">9</span><span style="line-height: 18.3999996185303px;"> April </span></b></p><p dir="ltr" sty